            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <a href="/Teams/Index" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Join a Team</a>
                    <p class="card-text">Register as a Cyclist and join one of our top-tier racing teams to compete in epic events.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="cta bg-primary text-white py-5 mt-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-3">Ready to race?</h2>
